### Example 17: A 3×3 Identity Matrix

The identity matrix has 1s on the diagonal, 0s elsewhere.

```scheme
(define I (matrix/identity 3))
I
```

<!-- BUILD: Prints ((1 0 0)(0 1 0)(0 0 1)). -->

[VISUAL: Text output; a 3×3 grid with 1s on the diagonal.]

