### Example 18: Matrix Addition

Add corresponding entries.

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 2)
                             (list 3 4))))
(define B (matrix/make (list (list 5 6)
                             (list 7 8))))
(matrix/+ A B)
```

<!-- BUILD: Prints ((6 8)(10 12)). -->

[VISUAL: Text output of the resulting matrix.]

