### Example 19: Scalar Multiplication

Multiply every entry by a scalar.

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 2)
                             (list 3 4))))
(matrix/scale A 2)
```

<!-- BUILD: Prints ((2 4)(6 8)). -->

[VISUAL: Text output.]

