### Example 20: Matrix Transpose

Flip rows and columns.

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 2 3)
                             (list 4 5 6))))
(matrix/transpose A)
```

<!-- BUILD: Prints ((1 4)(2 5)(3 6)), a 3×2 matrix. -->

[VISUAL: Text output showing the transposed shape.]

