### Example 21: Matrix Multiplication (2×2 times 2×2)

Matrix product: (AB)ᵢⱼ = Σₖ Aᵢₖ Bₖⱼ.

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 2)
                             (list 3 4))))
(define B (matrix/make (list (list 5 6)
                             (list 7 8))))
(matrix/* A B)
```

<!-- BUILD: Prints ((19 22)(43 50)), since (1×5+2×7, 1×6+2×8; 3×5+4×7, 3×6+4×8). -->

[VISUAL: Text output of the product matrix.]

